| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4548 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0f7a0632-af6b-5b8d-901b-b1ea6a61dbd2"
